name: 2D Game Assets Collection
description: Curated collection of 2D game assets from Kenney.nl, organized for easy use in kids' game development projects

platformer.name: Platformer
platformer.description: Assets for platform games including characters, tiles, items, and backgrounds. Features jumping characters, platform tiles, coins, and environmental elements.

rpg.name: Rpg
rpg.description: Role-playing game assets including dungeon tiles, characters, items, and environmental elements. Perfect for top-down RPG and roguelike games.

puzzle.name: Puzzle
puzzle.description: Puzzle game elements including blocks, crates, and interactive objects. Ideal for Sokoban-style puzzle games and brain teasers.

racing.name: Racing
racing.description: Racing game assets including various vehicles, road tiles, and racing-related objects. Great for top-down racing games.

space.name: Space
space.description: Space shooter assets including spaceships, backgrounds, and space-themed elements. Perfect for shoot-em-up and space adventure games.
